data.description: Beautiful Cape Cod home with over 2600 sf on large corner lot in the Beavercreek school district. Relax on your large covered front porch or on the back deck over looking the newly fenced back yard! Enter the front door and see all the recent renovations throughout the entire home. Gorgeous kitchen with tons of cabinets, quartz countertops, bar seating at the peninsula, and all appliances convey!  Large family room with barn door has access to the back yard and garage. Formal dining area open to the front living room with fireplace.  Two bedrooms and one full bath finish out the main level. Upstairs is one large bedroom with a full bath.  The lower level has the rec room, bedroom with egress window, laundry area and mechanicals room.  Driveway has access from Kemp and Rustic View with an extra parking pad area. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this home yours!
